title: Wall Street Breakfast June 17: Stock Futures Rebound After Brutal Selloff, But Will it Last?
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Stock futures rebound after brutal selloff, but will it last? Amazon loses legal battle over whether customers can sue over lack of toxic warnings. Number of high-quality refi candidates dwindles as mortgage rates rise: Black Knight. Musk meets Twitter staff, says 'Freedom of reach,' targeting 1B users are critical. Catch today’s WSB article here.
